# First, I will move to the coal and place a burner drill and a stone furnace next to it. Then, I will move to the iron ore and place another burner drill and stone furnace setup. We will use these to smelt some basic resources. I will also place an iron chest nearby to store these resources.
move_to(nearest('coal'));
place_entity('burner-drill', direction=2, position=nearest('coal'));
# Alright, we will attempt to use coordinates instead of 'nearest'.
move_to((-17, -14));
place_entity('burner-drill', direction=2, position=(-17, -14));
